# Aggressive dockerignore — only the market-maker workspace + its workspace
# metadata is needed. Everything else is excluded to keep the build context
# small. (The build context is uploaded to Fly's builder on every deploy.)

# By default ignore everything; whitelist what we need.
**

# Workspace root metadata
!package.json
!yarn.lock
!.yarnrc.yml
!.yarn

# Workspaces: include only their package.json so yarn install can resolve
# the workspace graph. Source for non-mm workspaces is not needed.
!core/package.json
!foundry/package.json

# Market-maker workspace itself
!market-maker
market-maker/node_modules
market-maker/dist
market-maker/.env
market-maker/.env.local
market-maker/logs
market-maker/data
market-maker/test

# Deploy assets used by the Dockerfile
!Dockerfile
!.dockerignore

# Common noise
**/*.log
**/.DS_Store
**/.git
**/.idea
**/.vscode
**/coverage
**/.next
